    "body": "I changed it to work on Windows only.\n\nThe issue also exists on OS X (as mentioned in #2945 and #1806). I believe the solution will be similar (normalizing the min/max size using `WindowSizeToFramelessSize` in the relevant views), but since I can't test it (no access to a Mac) I'll leave it to someone else.\n\nBy the way, the fix works for windows with or without a frame/border.\n"
